## Required for Multi-language Support

```env
# Google Cloud Translation API key.
# Obtain from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/translate.googleapis.com
GOOGLE_TRANSLATE_API_KEY=your_google_translate_api_key_here
```

## Optional

```env
# Public base URL of the deployed app (used for absolute links and OG tags).
# Default: http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-deployed-app.run.app
```

## Cloud Run / CI (Google Cloud Build substitutions)

Cloud Build substitution variables must be prefixed with `_`:

| Substitution variable     | Maps to env var              |
|---------------------------|------------------------------|
| `_GEMINI_API_KEY`         | `GEMINI_API_KEY`             |
| `_GOOGLE_TRANSLATE_KEY`   | `GOOGLE_TRANSLATE_API_KEY`   |
